and just this time-- it's

00:42:55.880 --> 00:42:56.700 align:middle line:90%
so expanding.

00:42:56.700 --> 00:42:59.000 align:middle line:84%
I could go back and go into
each one of the concepts

00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:00.500 align:middle line:84%
that I've learned
about-- perfection

00:43:00.500 --> 00:43:02.610 align:middle line:90%
