utterance of the soul.

00:43:17.540 --> 00:43:19.040 align:middle line:84%
And it's at the
heart of everything,

00:43:19.040 --> 00:43:20.414 align:middle line:84%
at the heart of
our conversation.

00:43:20.414 --> 00:43:22.200 align:middle line:84%
It's not the way
words are on a page.

00:43:22.200 --> 00:43:23.220 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's poetic.

00:43:23.220 --> 00:43:24.640 align:middle line:90%
>>NEPO: Yeah.

00:43:24.640 --> 00:43:28.616 align:middle line:84%
So yeah, this is a poem of
mine called "Free Fall."

00:43:28.616 --> 00:43:34.930 align:middle line:84%
"If you have one hour of
air and many hours to go,

00:43:34.930 --> 00:43:39.410 align:middle line:90%
you must breathe slowly.

00:43:39.410 --> 00:43:44.890 align:middle line:84%
If you have one arm's length
and many things to care for,

00:43:44.890 --> 00:43:48.380 align:middle line:90%
you must give freely.

00:43:48.380 --> 00:43:51.560 align:middle line:84%
If you have one chance to
know God, and many doubts,

00:43:51.560 --> 00:43:55.490 align:middle line:90%
you must set your heart on fire.

00:43:55.490 --> 00:43:57.050 align:middle line:90%
We are blessed.

00:43:57.050 --> 00:43:59.450 align:middle line:90%
Each day is a chance.

00:43:59.450 --> 00:44:01.950 align:middle line:90%
We have two arms.

00:44:01.950 --> 00:44:05.910 align:middle line:90%
Fear wastes air."

00:44:05.910 --> 00:44:06.820 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:44:06.820 --> 00:44:08.550 align:middle line:90%
Oh, chilling.

00:44:08.550 --> 00:44:09.400 align:middle line:90%
Beautiful.

00:44:09.400 --> 00:44:10.530 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:44:10.530 --> 00:44:11.320 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:44:11.320 --> 00:44:13.020 align:middle line:90%
When did you write that?

00:44:13.020 --> 00:44:16.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NEPO: I wrote that about a
year after my cancer journey.

00:44:16.300 --> 00:44:16.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:44:16.840 --> 00:44:19.040 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, that sums a lot of it up.

00:44:19.040 --> 00:44:20.970 align:middle line:84%
That's incred-- thank
you so much for sharing

00:44:20.970 --> 00:44:22.190 align:middle line:90%
